{"type":"text","timestamp":1781761935285,"sessionID":"ses_126b79683ffe1J61Cb0HgstWBi","part":{"id":"prt_ed9495daf001i8xlfyAskx60wZ","messageID":"msg_ed94947660012AhEyMxDCsX0eP","sessionID":"ses_126b79683ffe1J61Cb0HgstWBi","type":"text","text":"Resource loading surfaced the key constraint: this is a command-owned fan-out lineage, but this invocation is already the isolated lineage body with `artifact_dir` pre-bound. I’m skipping only the forbidden `resolveArtifactRoot` command as instructed, and preserving the deep-review state-machine files in the lineage directory.","time":{"start":1781761924527,"end":1781761935269},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08bcb2c40898519b016a33878482ec8191805f9cf9e8f39afb","phase":"commentary"}}}}
